        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This option can be combined with any other access control flags."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You typically use this constraint when you create a key pair and store the private key inside a deviceâ€™s Secure Enclave (by specifying the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/ksecattrtokenid"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " attribute with a value of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/ksecattrtokenidsecureenclave"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "). This makes the private key available for use in signing and verification tasks that happen inside the Secure Enclave with calls to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1618025-seckeyrawsign"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1617884-seckeyrawverify"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " functions. An attempt to use this constraint while generating a key pair outside the Secure Enclave fails. Similarly, an attempt to sign a block with a private key generated without this constraint inside the Secure Enclave fails."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
